WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(Default) {
color: #ffffffff;
font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
font-size: 020px;
text-shadow: #000000ff -2px 0px 2px, #000000ff 0px 2px 2px, #000000ff 0px -2px 2px, #000000ff 2px 0px 2px;
background-color: #00000000;
}

c0000000
00:00:01.080 --> 00:00:02.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Prepare yourselves.</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:04.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're next.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:04.590 --> 00:00:07.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I won't fail
at getting my revenge.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:08.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Alice?</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:09.430 --> 00:00:10.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh?</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:11.050 --> 00:00:12.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:13.310 --> 00:00:14.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're alive.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:14.390 --> 00:00:15.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:18.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska?</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:19.730 --> 00:00:20.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:21.060 --> 00:00:22.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:24.020 --> 00:00:26.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of all the times
to make an appearance.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:26.280 --> 00:00:28.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you have to show up now?</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:30.070 --> 00:00:32.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were rivals, but...</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:32.660 --> 00:00:34.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobs]
We can't call ourselves that.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:35.450 --> 00:00:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not anymore.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:38.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why not?</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:38.580 --> 00:00:40.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What does that even mean, huh?</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:40.210 --> 00:00:41.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never mind.
It's Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:41.750 --> 00:00:43.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-She's been--
-[ALICE] I told you to stay</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:43.540 --> 00:00:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-at the vacation house!
-Wha...?</b></Default>

c0000021
00:00:45.590 --> 00:00:47.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need you
to pay attention, here!</b></Default>

c0000022
00:00:47.590 --> 00:00:49.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your sister,
she's been kidnapped!</b></Default>

c0000023
00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:51.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vichyssoise escaped.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:00:51.220 --> 00:00:53.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She destroyed
Lou's vacation house!</b></Default>

c0000025
00:00:54.470 --> 00:00:55.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
She was kidnapped?</b></Default>

c0000026
00:00:56.520 --> 00:00:59.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was! I'm here
because I was chasing her!</b></Default>

c0000027
00:00:59.810 --> 00:01:01.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you being honest?</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:06.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if I wanted
to believe you, I just can't.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:06.940 --> 00:01:08.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because you work
for the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:09.490 --> 00:01:11.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I am the queen's daughter,</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:11.820 --> 00:01:14.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the princess in line
to take the throne.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:14.620 --> 00:01:16.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're saying Sisbell
was kidnapped, right?</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:17.240 --> 00:01:18.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, that sounds like
the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:19.290 --> 00:01:20.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>not like Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:20.960 --> 00:01:21.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You seem to know a lot,</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:23.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are you sure
you're not in on this?</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:24.210 --> 00:01:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
No, that's not...</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:25.500 --> 00:01:27.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's gotten into you?</b></Default>

c0000039
00:01:27.170 --> 00:01:28.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't be trusted!</b></Default>

c0000040
00:01:29.050 --> 00:01:31.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're an Imperial soldier,
Iska!</b></Default>

c0000041
00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:33.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000042
00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:35.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was standing right there.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:01:36.100 --> 00:01:37.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Elletear and Mother
were struck down,</b></Default>

c0000044
00:01:37.810 --> 00:01:39.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and there was nothing
I could do to save them.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:42.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By a Saint Disciple, like you!</b></Default>

c0000046
00:01:42.900 --> 00:01:43.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000047
00:01:43.940 --> 00:01:44.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?</b></Default>

c0000048
00:01:45.270 --> 00:01:47.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stop. There's no
coming back from this.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:01:48.190 --> 00:01:50.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My family
and my subordinates were hurt.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:01:51.820 --> 00:01:52.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
I'm crying.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:01:53.530 --> 00:01:56.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are tears streaming
down my face, but why?</b></Default>

c0000052
00:01:57.120 --> 00:01:59.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it because harm
has befallen my family?</b></Default>

c0000053
00:02:00.330 --> 00:02:01.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or because...</b></Default>

c0000054
00:02:03.210 --> 00:02:06.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am the second princess
of the Nebulis Sovereignty,</b></Default>

c0000055
00:02:06.380 --> 00:02:07.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aliceliese.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:02:08.050 --> 00:02:10.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I will destroy the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:02:10.380 --> 00:02:12.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if it means you fall.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:13.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:16.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Why? Just why?</b></Default>

c0000060
00:02:17.350 --> 00:02:18.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]
It's not fair!</b></Default>

c0000061
00:02:19.260 --> 00:02:21.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This isn't how I wanted
our rivalry to play out,</b></Default>

c0000062
00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:22.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>not like this!</b></Default>

c0000063
00:02:23.060 --> 00:02:24.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000064
00:02:27.980 --> 00:02:29.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Oh.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:02:29.440 --> 00:02:30.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, I get it.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:02:31.860 --> 00:02:33.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's probably
a good reason I'm crying.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:02:35.660 --> 00:02:37.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to forget about
the tension between</b></Default>

c0000068
00:02:37.570 --> 00:02:39.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Empire
and the Sovereignty,</b></Default>

c0000069
00:02:39.450 --> 00:02:41.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and watch our own
crusade play out.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:44.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least, that was my hope.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:46.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000072
00:02:52.420 --> 00:02:53.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Saint Disciple Iska.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:56.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is my declaration of war.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:02:56.970 --> 00:02:58.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're at war?</b></Default>

c0000075
00:02:58.550 --> 00:03:00.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice, please!
Now's not the time!</b></Default>

c0000076
00:03:01.350 --> 00:03:02.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're wrong.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:03:02.520 --> 00:03:03.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It has to be now.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:03:04.390 --> 00:03:06.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think I wanted to do this?</b></Default>

c0000079
00:03:07.650 --> 00:03:08.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ice breaks]</b></Default>

c0000080
00:03:09.310 --> 00:03:11.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is how
it has to end, here.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:13.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Whether we want it to or not!
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000082
00:03:13.610 --> 00:03:14.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
[swords clang]</b></Default>

c0000083
00:03:15.200 --> 00:03:16.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER]
Oh?</b></Default>

c0000084
00:03:16.820 --> 00:03:19.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is a shining beacon
of astral brilliance.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:03:20.240 --> 00:03:21.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shouldn't be surprised.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:24.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is Second Princess
Aliceliese.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:03:24.830 --> 00:03:27.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's Milla's daughter,
there's no denying it.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:03:28.250 --> 00:03:30.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And there's that
Imperial swordsman again.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:03:31.710 --> 00:03:33.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't understand.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:03:33.670 --> 00:03:35.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why is this swordsman
still puttering around</b></Default>

c0000091
00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:37.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the Sovereignty?</b></Default>

c0000092
00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:39.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He doesn't matter, though.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:03:40.760 --> 00:03:42.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Aliceliese.
-[wind gusting]</b></Default>

c0000094
00:03:42.760 --> 00:03:45.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't imagine the apple
fell far from the tree.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:03:46.230 --> 00:03:48.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're convinced
the Empire is behind this.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:03:48.730 --> 00:03:50.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The attacks
and the kidnapping.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:03:50.770 --> 00:03:52.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's it, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000098
00:03:54.320 --> 00:03:55.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[deep sigh]</b></Default>

c0000099
00:03:56.280 --> 00:03:57.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>History on repeat.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:03:58.160 --> 00:04:00.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a strange
and fateful destiny this is.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:04:01.910 --> 00:04:02.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000102
00:04:02.950 --> 00:04:04.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Salinger.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:04:04.580 --> 00:04:06.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must say,
you are astonishingly fit.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:04:07.410 --> 00:04:09.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does that mean
you're not too bright?</b></Default>

c0000105
00:04:09.370 --> 00:04:10.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000106
00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:12.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Here you lie at my feet,</b></Default>

c0000107
00:04:12.290 --> 00:04:13.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a heinous criminal
who stole more than</b></Default>

c0000108
00:04:14.050 --> 00:04:16.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>one-hundred astral spirits
in the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:04:16.880 --> 00:04:19.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that wasn't enough,
so you're after mine as well.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:04:19.890 --> 00:04:21.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You deserve to be
executed now.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:04:21.930 --> 00:04:24.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right here,
without trial nor jury.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:04:28.810 --> 00:04:29.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slurps]</b></Default>

c0000113
00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:33.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, this crusade
really was quite refreshing.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:04:33.770 --> 00:04:36.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And as such, I will spare
your life once again.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:04:37.240 --> 00:04:38.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER]
That's her?</b></Default>

c0000116
00:04:38.490 --> 00:04:40.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's next in line to be queen?</b></Default>

c0000117
00:04:41.110 --> 00:04:42.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000118
00:04:43.030 --> 00:04:44.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[battle grunts]</b></Default>

c0000119
00:04:45.450 --> 00:04:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000120
00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:48.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Salinger.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:50.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What was that?</b></Default>

c0000122
00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:52.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought brute force
was your whole thing?</b></Default>

c0000123
00:04:52.130 --> 00:04:53.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What will you do now?</b></Default>

c0000124
00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:55.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts]
-[electricity crackling]</b></Default>

c0000125
00:04:56.300 --> 00:04:57.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000126
00:04:59.470 --> 00:05:00.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

c0000127
00:05:00.680 --> 00:05:01.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that's it?</b></Default>

c0000128
00:05:01.800 --> 00:05:04.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your astral art is sloppy,
to say the least.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:05:05.100 --> 00:05:07.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] The strongest
contender for queen.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:05:08.140 --> 00:05:10.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Millavair Lou Nebulis VIII.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:05:11.560 --> 00:05:13.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was an emotionless
fighting machine.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:05:14.940 --> 00:05:16.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least, that had been
my impression.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:18.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Until that day.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:21.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's when I started
to see the real Milla.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:05:22.450 --> 00:05:23.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Salinger?</b></Default>

c0000136
00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:25.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:05:25.620 --> 00:05:26.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, it's you!</b></Default>

c0000138
00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000139
00:05:32.420 --> 00:05:33.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, what's so funny?</b></Default>

c0000140
00:05:35.540 --> 00:05:37.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Make it stop,
you're killing me!</b></Default>

c0000141
00:05:37.750 --> 00:05:38.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This might be the closest</b></Default>

c0000142
00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:40.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you've come to actually
beating me!</b></Default>

c0000143
00:05:40.590 --> 00:05:41.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughter]</b></Default>

c0000144
00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:44.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, what?</b></Default>

c0000145
00:05:44.930 --> 00:05:46.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, stop, please!</b></Default>

c0000146
00:05:47.010 --> 00:05:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big, buff Salinger,</b></Default>

c0000147
00:05:48.930 --> 00:05:50.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>walking down the street</b></Default>

c0000148
00:05:50.180 --> 00:05:52.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a couple of grocery bags
in his hands!</b></Default>

c0000149
00:05:52.310 --> 00:05:53.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000150
00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:55.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"You! Get ready,
because today is the day</b></Default>

c0000151
00:05:55.980 --> 00:05:57.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you kneel before me!"</b></Default>

c0000152
00:05:57.820 --> 00:05:59.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The same guy
who barks that at me</b></Default>

c0000153
00:05:59.440 --> 00:06:01.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a straight face
gets in line</b></Default>

c0000154
00:06:01.320 --> 00:06:02.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to check-out
with all the ladies.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:06:03.740 --> 00:06:05.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The thought of you
standing there with them</b></Default>

c0000156
00:06:05.450 --> 00:06:06.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is too much to bear!</b></Default>

c0000157
00:06:07.410 --> 00:06:09.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000158
00:06:09.620 --> 00:06:11.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Help!
My ribs are breaking!</b></Default>

c0000159
00:06:11.460 --> 00:06:12.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine, you win, all right?</b></Default>

c0000160
00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:14.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laugh continues]</b></Default>

c0000161
00:06:14.210 --> 00:06:15.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey. Milla!</b></Default>

c0000162
00:06:16.790 --> 00:06:18.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bag rustles]</b></Default>

c0000163
00:06:18.460 --> 00:06:20.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]
Huh. Hang on.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:06:20.460 --> 00:06:23.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You even managed
to get some discounted meat?</b></Default>

c0000165
00:06:23.470 --> 00:06:25.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm surprised
you have any limbs left</b></Default>

c0000166
00:06:25.390 --> 00:06:27.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after fending off those
cut-throat mommies!</b></Default>

c0000167
00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

c0000168
00:06:29.140 --> 00:06:30.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shut up!</b></Default>

c0000169
00:06:30.270 --> 00:06:32.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laugh continues]</b></Default>

c0000170
00:06:36.190 --> 00:06:39.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] The combat doll's
capable of laughing, too.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:06:39.780 --> 00:06:40.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[electricity crackles]</b></Default>

c0000172
00:06:41.070 --> 00:06:43.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even after our encounter
in the city,</b></Default>

c0000173
00:06:43.320 --> 00:06:46.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>our repartee on the battlefield
stayed the same.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:06:46.570 --> 00:06:48.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Discovering her sense of humor
wouldn't stop me.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:51.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I kept challenging her
as usual.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:06:51.910 --> 00:06:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But when did I start
feeling this way?</b></Default>

c0000177
00:06:55.210 --> 00:06:56.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These weren't
just fights anymore.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:06:57.000 --> 00:06:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was actually starting
to grow fond of them.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:07:00.210 --> 00:07:01.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What gives?</b></Default>

c0000180
00:07:01.670 --> 00:07:03.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you keep
repeating the same moves on me?</b></Default>

c0000181
00:07:04.130 --> 00:07:06.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're consistent,
I'll give you that.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:07:08.010 --> 00:07:09.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000183
00:07:09.760 --> 00:07:12.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER] As I'd lie there,
broken and defeated,</b></Default>

c0000184
00:07:12.770 --> 00:07:14.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>deep down, I'd find myself</b></Default>

c0000185
00:07:14.850 --> 00:07:17.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wishing our relationship
would never end. [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000186
00:07:17.940 --> 00:07:20.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unfortunately,
on that fateful night,</b></Default>

c0000187
00:07:20.820 --> 00:07:22.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everything fell apart.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:07:22.990 --> 00:07:24.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her majesty has been slain.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:07:26.150 --> 00:07:27.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000190
00:07:27.660 --> 00:07:28.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Salinger!</b></Default>

c0000191
00:07:29.910 --> 00:07:30.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was it...?</b></Default>

c0000192
00:07:31.700 --> 00:07:32.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was it you?</b></Default>

c0000193
00:07:33.250 --> 00:07:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Answer me!</b></Default>

c0000194
00:07:34.620 --> 00:07:36.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you strike down the queen?</b></Default>

c0000195
00:07:36.460 --> 00:07:39.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000196
00:07:39.790 --> 00:07:41.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000197
00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't just stand there!</b></Default>

c0000198
00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:46.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Salinger!</b></Default>

c0000199
00:07:47.130 --> 00:07:48.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would you do this?</b></Default>

c0000200
00:07:49.090 --> 00:07:49.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me!</b></Default>

c0000201
00:07:50.010 --> 00:07:52.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How could you do
something so vile?</b></Default>

c0000202
00:07:52.180 --> 00:07:54.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000203
00:07:55.060 --> 00:07:58.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All this time, I thought
you were only my rival,</b></Default>

c0000204
00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's it.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:07:59.860 --> 00:08:01.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And despite our circumstances,</b></Default>

c0000206
00:08:02.520 --> 00:08:05.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>well, I, I enjoyed our time.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:08:06.990 --> 00:08:08.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now this?</b></Default>

c0000208
00:08:08.700 --> 00:08:10.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why did you have to ruin it!</b></Default>

c0000209
00:08:10.320 --> 00:08:12.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000210
00:08:12.620 --> 00:08:14.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh. All this rage.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:08:14.660 --> 00:08:15.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just,</b></Default>

c0000212
00:08:16.290 --> 00:08:18.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to keep what we had.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:08:18.170 --> 00:08:22.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But now, I must fight you
like a proper enemy!</b></Default>

c0000214
00:08:23.630 --> 00:08:25.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER]
How ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:08:25.670 --> 00:08:28.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing has changed
in this world.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:08:28.840 --> 00:08:30.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thirty-seven years ago,</b></Default>

c0000217
00:08:30.180 --> 00:08:32.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hydra was behind
the assassination.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:08:32.430 --> 00:08:34.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just as they are right now!</b></Default>

c0000219
00:08:34.930 --> 00:08:37.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You two shouldn't be
wrapped up in this.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:08:37.270 --> 00:08:38.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The grudges, the betrayal,</b></Default>

c0000221
00:08:38.890 --> 00:08:41.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're too good
for these old tropes.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:08:42.230 --> 00:08:43.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The dynamic is nothing new.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:08:43.980 --> 00:08:46.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should've seen
this tragedy coming like</b></Default>

c0000224
00:08:46.150 --> 00:08:48.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a storm sweeping the horizon.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:08:48.650 --> 00:08:49.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a fool.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:08:50.700 --> 00:08:52.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you all learned nothing?</b></Default>

c0000227
00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:54.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Must you repeat
the mistakes of your past?</b></Default>

c0000228
00:08:55.740 --> 00:08:56.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Why this?</b></Default>

c0000229
00:08:56.950 --> 00:08:58.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When did it happen?</b></Default>

c0000230
00:08:58.620 --> 00:09:00.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How was our course
of fate disrupted?</b></Default>

c0000231
00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our factions are enemies,</b></Default>

c0000232
00:09:04.170 --> 00:09:05.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I thought
we had a connection</b></Default>

c0000233
00:09:05.670 --> 00:09:07.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that transcended our titles.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:09:08.050 --> 00:09:09.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ice crackling]</b></Default>

c0000235
00:09:10.050 --> 00:09:11.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts]
-[ice shatters]</b></Default>

c0000236
00:09:11.640 --> 00:09:13.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey!
Would ya listen to me!</b></Default>

c0000237
00:09:13.640 --> 00:09:15.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not here
to fight with you,</b></Default>

c0000238
00:09:15.100 --> 00:09:16.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm here to save Sisbell!</b></Default>

c0000239
00:09:16.470 --> 00:09:17.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't wanna hear it!</b></Default>

c0000240
00:09:18.230 --> 00:09:19.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't trust you.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:09:19.520 --> 00:09:20.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You Imperials have</b></Default>

c0000242
00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:22.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>breached the point
of no return!</b></Default>

c0000243
00:09:22.310 --> 00:09:23.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobs]</b></Default>

c0000244
00:09:23.560 --> 00:09:25.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This war will rage on.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:27.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unless one side meets
their end!</b></Default>

c0000246
00:09:29.070 --> 00:09:31.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You say that,
but do you really believe it?</b></Default>

c0000247
00:09:31.910 --> 00:09:34.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] It's what
the Sovereignty wants.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:09:34.950 --> 00:09:37.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This whole ordeal
has spiraled out of my control.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:40.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Attack me like
you're trying to kill me,</b></Default>

c0000250
00:09:40.870 --> 00:09:42.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>don't you dare hold back,
Iska!</b></Default>

c0000251
00:09:42.540 --> 00:09:43.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Alice!
-[ground cracking]</b></Default>

c0000252
00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:44.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The ground!</b></Default>

c0000253
00:09:45.210 --> 00:09:46.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000254
00:09:49.840 --> 00:09:51.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mirrors of ice?</b></Default>

c0000255
00:09:52.470 --> 00:09:54.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Will she attack me
with the ice?</b></Default>

c0000256
00:09:54.680 --> 00:09:55.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or trap me?</b></Default>

c0000257
00:09:56.470 --> 00:09:57.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, something's off.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:09:58.520 --> 00:10:00.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why all the reflections of me?</b></Default>

c0000259
00:10:00.770 --> 00:10:02.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should I break them,
one by one?</b></Default>

c0000260
00:10:02.850 --> 00:10:06.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ice Calamity, Rippling Light
in the Vast Dust!</b></Default>

c0000261
00:10:06.270 --> 00:10:08.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000262
00:10:08.730 --> 00:10:09.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000263
00:10:10.650 --> 00:10:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
So that's what they're for!</b></Default>

c0000264
00:10:12.280 --> 00:10:13.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000265
00:10:16.450 --> 00:10:17.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
As always...</b></Default>

c0000266
00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:20.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your instincts are super-human.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:10:21.250 --> 00:10:24.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I attacked them,
that would've been my end.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:10:24.710 --> 00:10:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
That's right.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:10:25.960 --> 00:10:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And knowing you,</b></Default>

c0000270
00:10:27.340 --> 00:10:28.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought destroying
those would be</b></Default>

c0000271
00:10:28.750 --> 00:10:30.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your first priority.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:10:30.510 --> 00:10:31.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was the trap I set.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:10:32.670 --> 00:10:34.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds like
it was specially designed</b></Default>

c0000274
00:10:34.300 --> 00:10:35.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to counter me.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:10:36.090 --> 00:10:38.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's because
it was, obviously.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:10:39.220 --> 00:10:40.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It wouldn't work
on anyone else.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:10:41.730 --> 00:10:44.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll really do
whatever it takes to win, huh?</b></Default>

c0000278
00:10:45.230 --> 00:10:47.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come at me
with everything you've got.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:10:47.270 --> 00:10:48.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Right now.
-[wind gusting]</b></Default>

c0000280
00:10:48.650 --> 00:10:50.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just like our battle
in the Nelka Forest.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:10:50.780 --> 00:10:51.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't hold back.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:10:51.820 --> 00:10:52.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:10:52.820 --> 00:10:53.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're nothing but a nameless</b></Default>

c0000284
00:10:54.030 --> 00:10:55.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Imperial swordsman to me now.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:58.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] [sighs]
Sisbell is in danger,</b></Default>

c0000286
00:10:58.370 --> 00:10:59.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to save her.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:10:59.790 --> 00:11:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm happy to spar it out
and resolve our problems.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:11:02.450 --> 00:11:04.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But does it have
to be right now?</b></Default>

c0000289
00:11:04.410 --> 00:11:05.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000290
00:11:05.710 --> 00:11:07.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need to get through!</b></Default>

c0000291
00:11:07.250 --> 00:11:09.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's only one way,
and you're blocking it!</b></Default>

c0000292
00:11:09.670 --> 00:11:13.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you wanna get through,
you'll have to strike me down!</b></Default>

c0000293
00:11:13.340 --> 00:11:16.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ISKA] Oh, crap!
-[ALICE] Great Ice Calamity!</b></Default>

c0000294
00:11:17.090 --> 00:11:18.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000295
00:11:20.180 --> 00:11:21.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
I knew you'd dodge it.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:11:21.520 --> 00:11:22.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000297
00:11:23.560 --> 00:11:24.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000298
00:11:25.140 --> 00:11:27.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] In the end,
I guess Rin was right.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:11:27.900 --> 00:11:29.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should have taken
her seriously.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:33.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She warned me that
one day the biggest threat</b></Default>

c0000301
00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:34.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd face would be you.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:37.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She told me not to open
my heart to you.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
I could say the same for you,</b></Default>

c0000304
00:11:41.950 --> 00:11:43.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in terms of threats.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:11:43.410 --> 00:11:45.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000306
00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:47.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:11:47.330 --> 00:11:48.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:11:50.630 --> 00:11:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go ahead, call me a witch.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:11:54.010 --> 00:11:55.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Say it.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:11:55.550 --> 00:11:57.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm an enemy
to the Imperial army.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:11:59.010 --> 00:12:00.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So please...</b></Default>

c0000312
00:12:00.180 --> 00:12:01.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if that's what I am to you.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:12:02.810 --> 00:12:04.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Say it.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:12:04.930 --> 00:12:05.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] [trembling]
Alice.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:12:06.640 --> 00:12:08.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your voice is trembling.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:12:09.020 --> 00:12:12.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not interested in those
who put themselves down.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:12:12.520 --> 00:12:13.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobs]</b></Default>

c0000318
00:12:14.070 --> 00:12:15.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's true.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:17.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing good
comes out of that.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:12:17.950 --> 00:12:19.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should know.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:12:19.450 --> 00:12:20.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Don't say it!</b></Default>

c0000322
00:12:21.030 --> 00:12:22.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not another word!</b></Default>

c0000323
00:12:22.120 --> 00:12:24.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please stop, don't say
anything nice to me!</b></Default>

c0000324
00:12:24.540 --> 00:12:26.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000325
00:12:26.960 --> 00:12:27.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From now on...</b></Default>

c0000326
00:12:28.040 --> 00:12:30.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need to act
as the princess of Nebulis.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:12:31.040 --> 00:12:32.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[weeping]
It's my duty.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:12:32.750 --> 00:12:34.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must destroy the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:12:35.090 --> 00:12:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So enough with the niceties.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:12:37.130 --> 00:12:39.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Forget about
everything we had,</b></Default>

c0000331
00:12:39.550 --> 00:12:41.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and just fight me already!</b></Default>

c0000332
00:12:41.890 --> 00:12:43.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ice Calamity.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:12:43.180 --> 00:12:44.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thousand Thorn Blizzard!</b></Default>

c0000334
00:12:46.890 --> 00:12:48.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Don't make me do this!</b></Default>

c0000335
00:12:48.520 --> 00:12:50.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The last thing
I want is to fight you,</b></Default>

c0000336
00:12:50.270 --> 00:12:51.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I will if I have to!</b></Default>

c0000337
00:12:52.190 --> 00:12:54.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No way I'm going easy
with that look in your eyes!</b></Default>

c0000338
00:12:55.070 --> 00:12:56.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do your worst, Iska!</b></Default>

c0000339
00:12:57.280 --> 00:12:58.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[battle grunts]</b></Default>

c0000340
00:13:03.120 --> 00:13:04.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From below?</b></Default>

c0000341
00:13:06.870 --> 00:13:08.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shatters]</b></Default>

c0000342
00:13:08.460 --> 00:13:09.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000343
00:13:09.670 --> 00:13:12.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000344
00:13:12.170 --> 00:13:13.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't hold back.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:13:13.750 --> 00:13:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's end this.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:13:15.300 --> 00:13:17.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am done
with prolonging the inevitable.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:13:18.260 --> 00:13:21.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will curse whatever
cruel fate invited this pain.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:13:21.930 --> 00:13:23.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With my own hands!</b></Default>

c0000349
00:13:23.930 --> 00:13:25.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SALINGER]
The destiny of stars.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:13:26.060 --> 00:13:27.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That this is a world
you would wish for,</b></Default>

c0000351
00:13:27.850 --> 00:13:29.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is truly perplexing.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:13:29.430 --> 00:13:32.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000353
00:13:32.150 --> 00:13:34.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What point is there
to continue witnessing</b></Default>

c0000354
00:13:34.110 --> 00:13:36.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the same mistake repeat itself?</b></Default>

c0000355
00:13:36.480 --> 00:13:38.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scoffs]
I refuse to watch this.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:13:38.570 --> 00:13:43.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000357
00:13:43.160 --> 00:13:45.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[battle grunts]</b></Default>

c0000358
00:13:46.450 --> 00:13:47.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Farewell, Iska!</b></Default>

c0000359
00:13:48.040 --> 00:13:49.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ice Calamity!</b></Default>

c0000360
00:13:53.130 --> 00:13:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That light!</b></Default>

c0000361
00:13:54.710 --> 00:13:56.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only when I activate
this ability</b></Default>

c0000362
00:13:57.050 --> 00:13:59.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>does my astral spirit
leave my body.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:13:59.630 --> 00:14:01.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and transfer itself
to this seed.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:14:02.130 --> 00:14:04.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're looking
at the manifestation</b></Default>

c0000365
00:14:04.390 --> 00:14:05.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of my astral spirit.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:14:06.470 --> 00:14:08.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] That's why
I couldn't pierce it.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:14:09.270 --> 00:14:10.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No more restraints.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:14:11.230 --> 00:14:12.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No more hiding.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:14:12.980 --> 00:14:14.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is goodbye!</b></Default>

c0000370
00:14:15.230 --> 00:14:16.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000371
00:14:16.980 --> 00:14:18.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000372
00:14:18.530 --> 00:14:23.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000373
00:14:23.610 --> 00:14:25.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Did she miss on purpose?</b></Default>

c0000374
00:14:27.530 --> 00:14:28.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:14:31.620 --> 00:14:32.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
What's the matter?</b></Default>

c0000376
00:14:33.250 --> 00:14:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come and fight me
with everything you've got!</b></Default>

c0000377
00:14:35.710 --> 00:14:38.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You missed. Again.
-[ALICE] Fight back!</b></Default>

c0000378
00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:40.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please.
Stop.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:14:40.510 --> 00:14:44.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000380
00:14:44.470 --> 00:14:45.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:47.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You could never hurt me.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:14:47.550 --> 00:14:48.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With those eyes.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:14:49.310 --> 00:14:50.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000384
00:14:56.440 --> 00:14:57.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:14:58.400 --> 00:14:59.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm really tired.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:15:00.070 --> 00:15:01.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aren't you?</b></Default>

c0000387
00:15:01.240 --> 00:15:03.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fighting out here
won't do us any good,</b></Default>

c0000388
00:15:03.150 --> 00:15:04.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or solve anything.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:15:04.820 --> 00:15:06.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll just end up
hurting each other.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:15:06.530 --> 00:15:07.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Understand?</b></Default>

c0000391
00:15:07.660 --> 00:15:09.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think
I want it to be this way?</b></Default>

c0000392
00:15:10.580 --> 00:15:11.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't!</b></Default>

c0000393
00:15:11.660 --> 00:15:14.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I can't forgive
the Imperial army!</b></Default>

c0000394
00:15:14.580 --> 00:15:17.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The army?
This is much bigger than them.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:15:17.790 --> 00:15:18.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh?</b></Default>

c0000396
00:15:18.790 --> 00:15:20.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Descendants of the Founder.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:15:20.550 --> 00:15:22.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People who share your blood.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:15:22.670 --> 00:15:25.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One of them is behind all this.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:15:25.590 --> 00:15:27.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's your sister,
Lady Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:15:28.510 --> 00:15:29.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, you're lying.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:15:30.140 --> 00:15:31.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Sisbell told me herself.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:35.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does that make her a liar, too?</b></Default>

c0000403
00:15:36.230 --> 00:15:37.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course not!</b></Default>

c0000404
00:15:37.690 --> 00:15:40.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska, she's my sister,
and I trust her!</b></Default>

c0000405
00:15:41.190 --> 00:15:42.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how do you expect me
to believe a word</b></Default>

c0000406
00:15:42.940 --> 00:15:44.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're saying right now?</b></Default>

c0000407
00:15:45.240 --> 00:15:48.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At first, I blamed Elletear
for betraying her people,</b></Default>

c0000408
00:15:48.120 --> 00:15:49.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I was wrong.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:15:49.950 --> 00:15:51.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The moment I saw her cut down.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:15:52.240 --> 00:15:53.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew it wasn't her.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:15:54.000 --> 00:15:56.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She protected our mother
with her own body.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:15:57.080 --> 00:15:59.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What if something else
is going on here?</b></Default>

c0000413
00:15:59.330 --> 00:16:01.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Something more?
-How dare you?</b></Default>

c0000414
00:16:01.090 --> 00:16:02.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So her sacrifice
means nothing to you--</b></Default>

c0000415
00:16:03.010 --> 00:16:04.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Please listen to me!
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000416
00:16:05.880 --> 00:16:07.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think about it, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:16:07.550 --> 00:16:09.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hydra reduced your manor
to nothing but rubble,</b></Default>

c0000418
00:16:09.890 --> 00:16:11.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we barely made it out.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:16:11.680 --> 00:16:13.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Talisman, the Vicious Tyrant,</b></Default>

c0000420
00:16:13.560 --> 00:16:15.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fights by enhancing
his combat skills</b></Default>

c0000421
00:16:15.770 --> 00:16:17.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>through the astral spirit
of waves.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:16:18.690 --> 00:16:19.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me I'm wrong.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:16:20.310 --> 00:16:21.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What I'm saying adds up.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:16:22.400 --> 00:16:23.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It does.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:16:24.110 --> 00:16:25.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
But?</b></Default>

c0000426
00:16:25.780 --> 00:16:26.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
That doesn't change the fact</b></Default>

c0000427
00:16:27.070 --> 00:16:28.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I still can't trust you.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:16:29.240 --> 00:16:31.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, who's to say you</b></Default>

c0000429
00:16:31.160 --> 00:16:32.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or someone else from the army</b></Default>

c0000430
00:16:32.450 --> 00:16:34.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>didn't research
Lord Talisman's astral spirit</b></Default>

c0000431
00:16:34.870 --> 00:16:36.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before you encountered him?</b></Default>

c0000432
00:16:36.910 --> 00:16:38.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if you're telling me
the truth,</b></Default>

c0000433
00:16:38.500 --> 00:16:40.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he'll use that as a cover story
if he's cornered.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:16:43.340 --> 00:16:46.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just can't trust the words
of an Imperial swordsman.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:16:46.760 --> 00:16:49.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not when this same man
couldn't protect my sister.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:16:50.090 --> 00:16:52.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hmm.
-For so long,</b></Default>

c0000437
00:16:52.760 --> 00:16:55.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have dreamed of measuring
my strength against yours.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:16:56.640 --> 00:16:58.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now, that day is here,</b></Default>

c0000439
00:16:58.690 --> 00:17:00.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and all I want
is anything but this.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:17:01.270 --> 00:17:04.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, there has to be
something I'm missing.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:17:05.820 --> 00:17:06.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:17:07.400 --> 00:17:08.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska, your wrist.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:17:09.240 --> 00:17:10.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000444
00:17:10.990 --> 00:17:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's glowing.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:17:12.280 --> 00:17:13.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
No way.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:17:14.370 --> 00:17:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] It's small, but
it's definitely an astral glow.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:17:17.290 --> 00:17:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't notice it
before during the fight,</b></Default>

c0000448
00:17:19.080 --> 00:17:22.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but since mine has dimmed,
it stands out so much.</b></Default>

c0000449
00:17:23.500 --> 00:17:24.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look, it's resonance!</b></Default>

c0000450
00:17:25.590 --> 00:17:26.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yumilecia.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:17:27.050 --> 00:17:29.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you-did you do
anything to her?</b></Default>

c0000452
00:17:30.430 --> 00:17:31.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like fight?</b></Default>

c0000453
00:17:31.840 --> 00:17:33.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Didn't lay a hand on her.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:17:33.600 --> 00:17:34.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I swear to you.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:17:35.260 --> 00:17:36.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
That's not what I meant.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:17:36.520 --> 00:17:39.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her astral spirit can
leave behind a message.</b></Default>

c0000457
00:17:40.140 --> 00:17:41.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A message?</b></Default>

c0000458
00:17:41.770 --> 00:17:43.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She can inscribe
with a single touch.</b></Default>

c0000459
00:17:44.230 --> 00:17:46.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Leaving the messenger
completely unaware if needed.</b></Default>

c0000460
00:17:47.320 --> 00:17:48.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:17:48.740 --> 00:17:51.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I fail you, you have
my permission to kill me.</b></Default>

c0000462
00:17:53.280 --> 00:17:54.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Iska.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:17:55.160 --> 00:17:56.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me unseal it.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:17:56.370 --> 00:17:57.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's all.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:18:00.250 --> 00:18:01.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:18:01.370 --> 00:18:03.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It activates
for the receiver with a touch.</b></Default>

c0000467
00:18:05.250 --> 00:18:06.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YUMILECIA]
Reporting.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:09.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We servants
of the royal family</b></Default>

c0000469
00:18:09.170 --> 00:18:12.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>hereby pledge that
this spirit reflects the truth.</b></Default>

c0000470
00:18:13.180 --> 00:18:15.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Empire isn't the only one</b></Default>

c0000471
00:18:15.300 --> 00:18:17.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>behind the Imperial
army's invasion.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:18:18.140 --> 00:18:20.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The mastermind behind
the coup is the Hydras.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:18:20.680 --> 00:18:23.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Their head, Talisman,
ambushed our manor</b></Default>

c0000474
00:18:23.150 --> 00:18:26.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>under the guise of mages
dressed as Imperials.</b></Default>

c0000475
00:18:26.690 --> 00:18:29.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The soldier in charge
of protecting Lady Sisbell</b></Default>

c0000476
00:18:29.150 --> 00:18:30.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>defended our lives,</b></Default>

c0000477
00:18:30.610 --> 00:18:32.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and is attempting
to safely recover her.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:18:32.990 --> 00:18:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, show the four soldiers
your kindness and compassion.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:18:37.410 --> 00:18:38.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That settles it.</b></Default>

c0000480
00:18:39.750 --> 00:18:41.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like the princess
was deceived.</b></Default>

c0000481
00:18:42.710 --> 00:18:45.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you were right, all along.</b></Default>

c0000482
00:18:52.550 --> 00:18:54.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]
What is wrong with me?</b></Default>

c0000483
00:18:54.590 --> 00:18:56.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so sorry, Iska!</b></Default>

c0000484
00:18:56.680 --> 00:18:59.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I wanted
was to protect my family!</b></Default>

c0000485
00:18:59.310 --> 00:19:00.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To do right by everyone!</b></Default>

c0000486
00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:03.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is my fault!</b></Default>

c0000487
00:19:04.060 --> 00:19:06.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did such a horrible
thing to you!</b></Default>

c0000488
00:19:06.270 --> 00:19:07.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Stand up, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:19:08.900 --> 00:19:10.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think I traveled
all the way here</b></Default>

c0000490
00:19:10.610 --> 00:19:12.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to decide the future
of the Sovereignty?</b></Default>

c0000491
00:19:13.070 --> 00:19:13.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

c0000492
00:19:14.070 --> 00:19:15.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm here to protect Sisbell,</b></Default>

c0000493
00:19:16.320 --> 00:19:17.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she's counting on me.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:19:18.660 --> 00:19:20.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What, are you gonna
sit here all night?</b></Default>

c0000495
00:19:21.250 --> 00:19:23.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Cry?
Then, I'm leaving.</b></Default>

c0000496
00:19:23.790 --> 00:19:25.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
You're unbelievable.</b></Default>

c0000497
00:19:34.300 --> 00:19:36.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here I am,
pouring my heart out to you.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:19:37.220 --> 00:19:40.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you can't think
of one nice thing to say to me?</b></Default>

c0000499
00:19:40.350 --> 00:19:42.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did it cross your mind
to offer a hand?</b></Default>

c0000500
00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:45.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Empire can be so uncivil!</b></Default>

c0000501
00:19:46.730 --> 00:19:49.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're free to be
disappointed, but...</b></Default>

c0000502
00:19:51.940 --> 00:19:53.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:19:56.530 --> 00:19:57.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

c0000504
00:19:58.160 --> 00:20:00.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For refusing to treat me
any differently.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:20:01.410 --> 00:20:04.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Words can't describe
how happy I am.</b></Default>

c0000506
00:20:04.540 --> 00:20:07.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That you still see me
as your equal and your rival.</b></Default>

c0000507
00:20:09.210 --> 00:20:10.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Alice?</b></Default>

c0000508
00:20:13.050 --> 00:20:14.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000509
00:20:26.640 --> 00:20:27.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am sincere.</b></Default>

c0000510
00:20:29.020 --> 00:20:30.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:20:30.940 --> 00:20:34.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000512
00:20:34.690 --> 00:20:35.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even so...</b></Default>

c0000513
00:20:35.740 --> 00:20:37.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I resent the army
for the chaos</b></Default>

c0000514
00:20:37.320 --> 00:20:38.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>caused at the manor.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:20:38.700 --> 00:20:41.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As for that Saint Disciple,
he'll pay dearly.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:20:42.530 --> 00:20:44.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So mark my words.</b></Default>

c0000517
00:20:44.120 --> 00:20:46.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My rage will never be
yours to bear again.</b></Default>

c0000518
00:20:47.290 --> 00:20:48.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll go after the Hydras.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:20:49.120 --> 00:20:51.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You shelter somewhere safe
with the servants.</b></Default>

c0000520
00:20:51.250 --> 00:20:53.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sirens wailing in distance]</b></Default>

c0000521
00:20:55.460 --> 00:20:57.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That sounds like the med team.</b></Default>

c0000522
00:20:57.550 --> 00:20:58.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go, quickly.</b></Default>

c0000523
00:21:00.220 --> 00:21:01.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>On it.</b></Default>

c0000524
00:21:03.600 --> 00:21:04.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ALICE] Hey.
-Hm?</b></Default>

c0000525
00:21:06.770 --> 00:21:10.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you're not
the worst guy I could like.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:21:11.610 --> 00:21:12.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000527
00:21:14.110 --> 00:21:15.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh!
Hang on!</b></Default>

c0000528
00:21:15.780 --> 00:21:17.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't get the wrong idea!</b></Default>

c0000529
00:21:17.400 --> 00:21:19.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I say, "like"
I mean "like as a rival!"</b></Default>

c0000530
00:21:20.570 --> 00:21:22.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, quit staring at me already!</b></Default>

c0000531
00:21:22.910 --> 00:21:24.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am being
so serious right now!</b></Default>

c0000532
00:21:27.120 --> 00:21:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, you could've fooled me!</b></Default>

c0000533
00:21:28.660 --> 00:21:33.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000534
00:21:33.210 --> 00:21:34.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000535
00:21:34.380 --> 00:21:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Funny.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:21:35.550 --> 00:21:36.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For a second, I thought</b></Default>

c0000537
00:21:36.550 --> 00:21:38.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you had a new trap
up your sleeve.</b></Default>

c0000538
00:21:38.720 --> 00:21:40.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, what are you implying?</b></Default>

c0000539
00:21:40.340 --> 00:21:42.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you were waiting
for me to seduce you,</b></Default>

c0000540
00:21:42.300 --> 00:21:43.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then think again, creep!</b></Default>

c0000541
00:21:44.510 --> 00:21:45.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh.
Whatever.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:21:46.310 --> 00:21:47.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Get out of my sight.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:21:48.020 --> 00:21:49.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bye, then!</b></Default>

c0000544
00:21:50.600 --> 00:21:52.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Consider yourself lucky, Iska.</b></Default>

c0000545
00:21:54.440 --> 00:21:55.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're off the hook.</b></Default>

c0000546
00:21:55.570 --> 00:21:58.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But next time, we'll
definitely settle the score.</b></Default>

c0000547
00:22:00.990 --> 00:22:03.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So watch out!</b></Default>

c0000548
00:22:04.370 --> 00:22:05.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Next time," huh?</b></Default>

c0000549
00:22:05.830 --> 00:22:06.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:22:09.000 --> 00:22:10.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Next time!</b></Default>

c0000551
00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:16.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] When the sun hides
beneath the cloak of night,</b></Default>

c0000552
00:22:16.630 --> 00:22:19.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the moon stands
sentinel overhead.</b></Default>

c0000553
00:22:19.260 --> 00:22:20.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000554
00:22:21.590 --> 00:22:23.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The one who invited
the Imperial army</b></Default>

c0000555
00:22:24.050 --> 00:22:26.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is your master,
Talisman, correct?</b></Default>

c0000556
00:22:28.430 --> 00:22:30.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And he orchestrated
the last attempt</b></Default>

c0000557
00:22:30.430 --> 00:22:31.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on the queen's life.</b></Default>

c0000558
00:22:31.770 --> 00:22:33.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You Hydras skulk
in the shadows</b></Default>

c0000559
00:22:33.900 --> 00:22:35.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until you make your move.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:22:36.360 --> 00:22:38.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or maybe some things
about this world</b></Default>

c0000561
00:22:38.150 --> 00:22:40.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are better kept
under the radar.</b></Default>

c0000562
00:22:40.900 --> 00:22:43.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] Does this have to do
with your transformation</b></Default>

c0000563
00:22:43.660 --> 00:22:45.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into that vile creature?</b></Default>

c0000564
00:22:45.490 --> 00:22:47.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[laughs]
-Monster or mage,</b></Default>

c0000565
00:22:47.370 --> 00:22:49.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it matters little to me
what form you take.</b></Default>

c0000566
00:22:49.870 --> 00:22:52.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You will not scuttle away
from my sight.</b></Default>

c0000567
00:22:52.330 --> 00:22:55.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As thrilling as that sounds,
I'm busy.</b></Default>

c0000568
00:22:55.670 --> 00:22:57.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So call me
when I'm not playing</b></Default>

c0000569
00:22:57.090 --> 00:22:59.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>babysitter, ya old geezer.</b></Default>

c0000570
00:22:59.510 --> 00:23:01.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here, I'll toss you
to someone else</b></Default>

c0000571
00:23:01.420 --> 00:23:02.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who's dying to play.</b></Default>

c0000572
00:23:03.050 --> 00:23:05.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A big, bad, witch,
all to yourself.</b></Default>

c0000573
00:23:05.680 --> 00:23:06.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[creepy laughter]
-What?</b></Default>

c0000574
00:23:07.550 --> 00:23:09.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[creepy laughter]</b></Default>

c0000575
00:23:09.390 --> 00:23:11.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have fun, old man.</b></Default>

c0000576
00:23:11.520 --> 00:23:12.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind gusting]</b></Default>

c0000577
00:23:14.060 --> 00:23:16.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] I feel you lurking,
demonic fiend.</b></Default>

c0000578
00:23:16.560 --> 00:23:17.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Show yourself!</b></Default>

c0000579
00:23:17.860 --> 00:23:20.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[creepy laughter]</b></Default>

c0000580
00:23:21.280 --> 00:23:23.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you truly a witch?</b></Default>

c0000581
00:23:24.610 --> 00:23:26.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SUBJECT E]
Won't you listen now,</b></Default>

c0000582
00:23:26.320 --> 00:23:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the requiem of the stars?</b></Default>

c0000583
00:23:31.910 --> 00:23:33.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MESSENGER 209A]
The message is as follows.</b></Default>

c0000584
00:23:34.120 --> 00:23:36.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Complete bed rest count one.</b></Default>

c0000585
00:23:36.880 --> 00:23:38.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Queen Millavair
Lou Nebulis VIII.</b></Default>

c0000586
00:23:39.420 --> 00:23:41.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No life-threatening injuries,</b></Default>

c0000587
00:23:42.460 --> 00:23:44.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Missing persons count, three.</b></Default>

c0000588
00:23:44.380 --> 00:23:46.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Head of Zoa, Growley.</b></Default>

c0000589
00:23:46.340 --> 00:23:47.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whereabouts unknown.</b></Default>

c0000590
00:23:48.100 --> 00:23:50.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Currently seeking
any witnesses.</b></Default>

c0000591
00:23:50.970 --> 00:23:53.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The First Princess of Lou,
Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000592
00:23:54.180 --> 00:23:56.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kidnapped by the Imperial army.</b></Default>

c0000593
00:23:57.440 --> 00:24:00.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Third Princess of Lou,
Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000594
00:24:00.610 --> 00:24:03.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kidnapped by the Imperial army
at the Lou's manor.</b></Default>

c0000595
00:24:05.280 --> 00:24:06.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000596
00:24:14.580 --> 00:24:17.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait.
What happened, where am I?</b></Default>

c0000597
00:24:17.960 --> 00:24:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska?</b></Default>

c0000598
00:24:20.340 --> 00:24:21.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Captain Mismis?</b></Default>

c0000599
00:24:21.840 --> 00:24:22.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nene?</b></Default>

c0000600
00:24:23.010 --> 00:24:24.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Jhin?</b></Default>

c0000601
00:24:27.260 --> 00:24:28.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one's here.</b></Default>

c0000602
00:24:29.140 --> 00:24:31.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Last thing I remember
is being in the manor,</b></Default>

c0000603
00:24:31.260 --> 00:24:32.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which means...</b></Default>

c0000604
00:24:33.390 --> 00:24:35.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those Hydras kidnapped me!</b></Default>

c0000605
00:24:35.390 --> 00:24:37.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do they seriously believe
this'll break me?</b></Default>

c0000606
00:24:40.060 --> 00:24:41.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Nice try.</b></Default>

c0000607
00:24:41.270 --> 00:24:42.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I won't break.</b></Default>

c0000608
00:24:42.400 --> 00:24:43.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't!</b></Default>

c0000609
00:24:43.900 --> 00:24:46.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I don't believe in them,
then who else will?</b></Default>

c0000610
00:24:50.530 --> 00:24:53.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Astral spirits
that guide this planet.</b></Default>

c0000611
00:24:53.490 --> 00:24:55.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, hear my prayer.</b></Default>

c0000612
00:24:56.040 --> 00:24:59.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let my voice reach
through to their hearts!</b></Default>

